{"TopicId":101902,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"how to vtol","CreatedByName":"jake9039","CreatedById":122602,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-13T23:38:02Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"jake9039","CreatedById":122602,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-13T23:38:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI have a question. how do I make a vtol? all mine will start out fine, but then either they do all the flips or don\u0027t even take off.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-03-14T03:02:17Z\u0022 title=\u002203/14/2015 03:02  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 14, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by jake9039\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Espelling error\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WARodst10175","CreatedById":136962,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-13T23:46:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EBasicly you get Kerbal Foundries. Thank me later.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jake9039","CreatedById":122602,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-14T00:09:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI do have kerbal foundaries, but I just mean in stock. I want to be able to share my craft with people.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-14T00:27:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAlso get TCA: Throttle Controlled Avionics = no more fighting off-balance designs\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Taki117","CreatedById":89975,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-14T00:30:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThere\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/13XSzUogxo8?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnd\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/iMi77hLvROw?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mad Rocket Scientist","CreatedById":139256,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-14T01:25:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAssuming the center of thrust is aligned with the center of mass, make sure that fuel tanks are draining correctly (occasionally when attaching fuel lines in symmetry one won\u0027t connect) and that there are little to no off center wings i.e. there isn\u0027t to much drag on one half of the VTOL.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDisclaimer:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI am terrible at building jet VTOLs and only okay with rocket VTOLs.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EGood luck and I hope this was helpful!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jake9039","CreatedById":122602,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-14T01:32:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Eok. I will look at what was suggested, and I will report what I come up with asakp\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mister Dilsby","CreatedById":232743,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-14T01:44:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMy entry in this challenge \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/111664-The-Excursion-to-Mt-Keverest/page4\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/111664-The-Excursion-to-Mt-Keverest/page4\u003C/a\u003E \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E...is one way to do it in stock, with monopropellant thrusters. The imgur gallery shows some details of how I made sure the center of mass was aligned with center of thrust for the VTOL system, and how I managed fuel flow to ensure that center of mass would not move around when I was in VTOL mode. Note that RCS and SAS motors are used to stabilize the system in VTOL flight.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERockets and jets make more efficient VTOL lifters. Jets are very hard to control because of the lag time in controlling thrust. Good luck!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"jake9039","CreatedById":122602,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-14T03:02:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ethe mods really helped.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wanderfound","CreatedById":112611,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-14T05:05:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EVids of one of my VTOL builds and testflights:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/YTlBGSDeuec?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/whVQQ282Fbg?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/5pCJa4rrnfE?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n"}]}